  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Discussion On Making All Things Equal
---
Shun replied, "These three rulers are only little dwellers in the weeds
and brush. Why this nagging desire? Long ago, ten suns came out all at
once and the ten thousand things were all lighted up. And how much
greater is virtue than these suns!"
